data.description: Gorgeous 4-bedroom, 2-bath and 2 car garage home. It features a spacious kitchen with modern QUARTZ countertops and  stainless steel appliances. The flooring has been updated with premium materials, including ceramic tile and laminate in the bedrooms. The master suite is especially remarkable, offering wooden flooring, his and hers walk-in closets, and his and hers vanities, along with a shower and a luxurious Roman spa tub. Both the interior and exterior of the home have recently been painted in neutral colors. The large backyard includes a covered patio, perfect for entertaining guests. The home is situated in a beautiful family-oriented neighborhood, within close proximity to schools and shopping areas. This remarkable family home is definitely worth a visit!
